{"id":2703,"date":"2023-10-13T09:19:14","date_gmt":"2023-10-13T02:19:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2703"},"modified":"2023-10-13T09:19:14","modified_gmt":"2023-10-13T02:19:14","slug":"dang-ky-cap-nhat-kien-thuc-chuyen-mon-duoc-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/dang-ky-cap-nhat-kien-thuc-chuyen-mon-duoc-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u0102NG K\u00dd C\u1eacP NH\u1eacT KI\u1ebeN TH\u1ee8C CHUY\u00caN M\u00d4N D\u01af\u1ee2C T\u1ea0I TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1edbp c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n D\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p <\/span><\/i><b><i>\u201cGi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 D\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Y T\u1ebf.<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd h\u1ebft hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c l\u1edbp c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n D\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh trong Lu\u1eadt D\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m 2016 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 kinh doanh thu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea1m vi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Y t\u1ebf.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3 D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf kinh doanh d\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u1eb7c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ho\u00e0n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb thu h\u1ed3i Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1ee3c. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1edf L\u1edbp c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n D\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i Th\u00e1ng 11.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\ud83d\udcd1 \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u1ea1i:<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.gle\/FyhnyGF2rT6ZAtBQ6\"> <b>Form \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd<\/b><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">** Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn: <\/span><b>12\/10\/2023 \u0111\u1ebfn 24\/11\/2023<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\ud83d\udcc6 Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o: <\/span><b>8h00 &#8211; 17h30, Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 26\/11\/2023<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">** H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c: <\/span><b>Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn (online)<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd bao g\u1ed3m:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean quan;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ee5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ee5p b\u1eb1ng T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ee5p CMT\/CCCD.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn qua \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 Email tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 24\/11\/2023. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p <\/span><b>ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Email v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7.<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tham gia 80% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ea1t 50%.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 600.000 \u0111\/h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean\/kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i dung, th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y:<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1UE91a7BVeK6gBakzIDeCqOvuJLVSMMTz\/view?usp=drive_link\"><b> Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o L\u1edbp c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u00e1ng 1<\/b><b>1<\/b><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft\u00a0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 theo \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Ph\u00f2ng \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u2013 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>